Quickstrike:




Quickstrike leaned back. "Ah don't need yer protection." He looked 
back at Dark Mouse. He needed to talk to Black Aracnia about this as 
soon as he could get to her.

He got out with the others as the pod landed. He gave Dark Mouse and 
glance.
